WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

2
00:01:59.703 --> 00:02:02.289
- Good morrow. lady rhea.
- Cousin.

3
00:02:02.372 --> 00:02:04.333
What's today's quarry? Rabbit?

4
00:02:04.833 --> 00:02:07.961
-Deen -oh. fine challenge.

5
00:02:08.045 --> 00:02:09.504
Care for some company?

6
00:02:09.588 --> 00:02:10.881
I'd rather ride alone.

7
00:02:13.300 --> 00:02:14.551
Good fortune to you.

8
00:03:01.723 --> 00:03:02.808
Husband.

9
00:03:08.355 --> 00:03:09.606
What brings you to the vale?

10
00:03:14.194 --> 00:03:18.156
Or have you at last come
to consummate our marriage?

11
00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:22.244
The vale's sheep might be willing.

12
00:03:22.327 --> 00:03:23.787
even if I'm not.

13
00:03:24.663 --> 00:03:27.541
Our sheep are prettier. after all.

14
00:03:29.042 --> 00:03:32.754
Or perhaps your brother has at last
had his fill of your company.

15
00:03:33.797 --> 00:03:36.758
Cast you aside
in favor of a little girl.

16
00:03:42.931 --> 00:03:44.516
What will you do now?

17
00:03:45.475 --> 00:03:48.603
Will you strike the child down?

18
00:03:48.687 --> 00:03:49.980
Or?

19
00:04:39.237 --> 00:04:41.114
I knew you couldn't finish.

20
00:04:43.033 --> 00:04:44.242
Craven!

21
00:05:24.157 --> 00:05:25.575
Thank you.

22
00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:08.368
A moment.

23
00:06:15.792 --> 00:06:17.168
I do not wish to see you go.

24
00:06:20.213 --> 00:06:22.132
Such is the king's decision.

25
00:06:22.215 --> 00:06:23.967
A decision I most bitterly regret.

26
00:06:27.012 --> 00:06:29.014
And yet. you made it possible.

27
00:06:31.224 --> 00:06:32.726
You chose rhaenyra.

28
00:06:34.185 --> 00:06:35.729
She swore her innocence.

29
00:06:35.812 --> 00:06:37.355
and I believed her.

30
00:06:37.439 --> 00:06:40.442
You wanted to believe her.
as did her father.

31
00:06:40.525 --> 00:06:41.943
Your informant was wrong.

32
00:06:42.027 --> 00:06:44.863
An honest mistake. perhaps.
but I did not foresee this!

33
00:06:44.946 --> 00:06:46.531
You should have.

34
00:06:46.615 --> 00:06:49.784
If you had not been so relentless
in advancing aegon as heir!

35
00:07:00.462 --> 00:07:01.755
Listen to me. daughter.

36
00:07:03.131 --> 00:07:05.175
The king will die.

37
00:07:05.258 --> 00:07:08.553
It may be months or years.
but he'll not live to be an old man.

38
00:07:08.637 --> 00:07:10.597
And if rhaenyra succeeds him.

39
00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:14.017
war will follow. do you understand?

40
00:07:14.100 --> 00:07:15.894
The realm will not accept her.

41
00:07:15.977 --> 00:07:17.479
And to secure her claim.

42
00:07:17.562 --> 00:07:20.231
she'll have to put
your children to the sword.

43
00:07:20.315 --> 00:07:21.608
She'll have no choice.

44
00:07:24.611 --> 00:07:26.321
You know it.

45
00:07:26.404 --> 00:07:30.075
You're no fool.
and yet you choose not to see it.

46
00:07:32.327 --> 00:07:34.454
The time is coming. alicent.

47
00:07:35.914 --> 00:07:38.416
Either you prepare aegon to rule.

48
00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:42.712
or you cleave to rhaenyra
and pray for her mercy.

49
00:09:15.972 --> 00:09:19.559
Where is lord corlys?
He should be here to receive the king.

50
00:09:28.485 --> 00:09:29.819
Welcome to high tide. your grace.

51
00:09:31.112 --> 00:09:33.323
What is the meaning of this. lady laena?

52
00:09:34.115 --> 00:09:36.117
Is this how house velaryon
greets its king?

53
00:09:37.243 --> 00:09:40.038
My father has but just returned
from his long journey

54
00:09:40.789 --> 00:09:44.042
and he has hastened to the hall of nine
to await your grace's arrival.

55
00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:49.631
Let's just get on with it.

56
00:09:59.265 --> 00:10:00.725
An outsider...

57
00:10:01.726 --> 00:10:03.019
Among the natives.

58
00:10:04.270 --> 00:10:05.480
Lord larys.

59
00:10:07.232 --> 00:10:08.650
Malvales.

60
00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:10.276
A rare bloom.

61
00:10:11.778 --> 00:10:14.280
Indigenous to braavos.

62
00:10:16.407 --> 00:10:20.078
By all rights.
it shouldn't be thriving here.

63
00:10:20.954 --> 00:10:23.706
Nature. such mystery.

64
00:10:25.041 --> 00:10:26.960
- The weather has been lovely.
- Indeed.

65
00:10:27.043 --> 00:10:28.878
And yet it is a dark day for the realm.

66
00:10:33.007 --> 00:10:34.259
Your father was a good man.

67
00:10:36.970 --> 00:10:38.471
As is yours who took his place.

68
00:10:42.433 --> 00:10:43.643
Yet still.

69
00:10:44.269 --> 00:10:46.896
the manner of your father's departure...

70
00:10:48.189 --> 00:10:50.775
It feels something of an injustice.

71
00:10:52.569 --> 00:10:54.737
What do you know of the matter
of his leaving?

72
00:10:54.821 --> 00:10:56.531
When one is never invited to speak.

73
00:10:56.614 --> 00:11:00.368
one learns instead to... observe.

74
00:11:02.662 --> 00:11:04.247
You're perhaps in need of an ally?

75
00:11:05.290 --> 00:11:06.499
I'm the queen.

76
00:11:06.583 --> 00:11:09.002
- I have no shortage of allies.
- Naturally.

77
00:11:09.085 --> 00:11:11.087
Princess rhaenyra. for example.

78
00:11:12.505 --> 00:11:14.132
State your purpose. my lord.

79
00:11:17.886 --> 00:11:20.889
I did wonder if she could be relied upon

80
00:11:20.972 --> 00:11:23.600
now that she is unwell.

81
00:11:25.059 --> 00:11:28.146
Unwell? I haven't heard anything.

82
00:11:28.897 --> 00:11:30.940
Begging your pardon.
your grace. I may be mistaken.

83
00:11:32.609 --> 00:11:35.236
It's just that on the very same night
your father was dismissed.

84
00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:38.948
the grand maester delivered a tea
to the Princess's chambers.

85
00:11:41.075 --> 00:11:43.077
- A tea?
- Yes.

86
00:11:45.872 --> 00:11:48.082
That the grand maester himself brought?

87
00:11:48.166 --> 00:11:51.377
At the direction of the king.
as I understand it.

88
00:11:54.130 --> 00:11:56.341
I do hope she's not unwell.

89
00:11:57.842 --> 00:12:00.011
Rhaenyra sailed
with the king to driftmark

90
00:12:00.094 --> 00:12:02.513
- yesterday at daybreak.
- Oh. what good news.

91
00:12:03.181 --> 00:12:04.390
I must've been in error.

92
00:12:05.975 --> 00:12:07.936
Ah. a relief.

93
00:12:09.812 --> 00:12:12.023
I thought for mellos himself. well...

94
00:12:13.650 --> 00:12:15.652
Her condition must be
something very serious.

95
00:12:16.903 --> 00:12:19.906
What happiness it is to have been wrong.

96
00:12:50.728 --> 00:12:51.896
I'm sorry.

97
00:12:51.980 --> 00:12:53.314
Come. cousin.

98
00:12:53.398 --> 00:12:56.025
Let us discover what might be had
for breakfast.

99
00:13:29.434 --> 00:13:30.852
Your grace.

100
00:13:45.783 --> 00:13:47.785
Rise. lord corlys.

101
00:13:49.245 --> 00:13:50.538
Be welcome.

102
00:13:50.621 --> 00:13:52.248
May I offer you a chair?

103
00:13:54.083 --> 00:13:55.168
Cousin!

104
00:13:56.544 --> 00:13:57.920
Princess.

105
00:14:05.553 --> 00:14:07.764
- Are you well?
- Very.

106
00:14:08.931 --> 00:14:10.933
I congratulate you. lord lyonel.

107
00:14:11.017 --> 00:14:14.228
I can think of no man more suited to be
the hand of the king.

108
00:14:14.312 --> 00:14:17.023
That is very kind of you to say.
lord corlys.

109
00:14:17.106 --> 00:14:19.108
His grace has honored me with the post.

110
00:14:21.486 --> 00:14:22.820
Pity about ser Otto.

111
00:14:25.365 --> 00:14:28.659
Despite spending most of my days
amidst the grandeur of the red keep.

112
00:14:28.743 --> 00:14:31.621
the halls of high tide
never fail to impress.

113
00:14:31.704 --> 00:14:33.373
You flatter me. your grace.

114
00:14:34.374 --> 00:14:37.043
Though I do wish we could meet
under happier pretenses.

115
00:14:38.586 --> 00:14:41.047
- How so?
- Daemon's wife.

116
00:14:41.130 --> 00:14:43.257
the lady rhea Royce. has passed.

117
00:14:44.258 --> 00:14:45.698
A hunting mishap.

118
00:14:46.677 --> 00:14:48.679
She was thrown from her horse.

119
00:14:48.763 --> 00:14:51.849
Her neck and skull
both crushed in the fall.

120
00:14:51.933 --> 00:14:54.185
A most surprising end.

121
00:14:54.268 --> 00:14:58.606
Lady rhea's skill as both
rider and hunter were well-known.

122
00:14:58.689 --> 00:15:00.942
- The gods are cruel.
- 4ndeed.

123
00:15:01.818 --> 00:15:07.115
Lady rhea was a fine woman
and a good wife to my brother.

124
00:15:07.198 --> 00:15:11.035
Sad thing that she and daemon
have no heirs to succeed her.

125
00:15:11.119 --> 00:15:12.829
She stood to inherit runestone.

126
00:15:13.955 --> 00:15:17.166
Mayhaps we can turn toward
happier pursuits.

127
00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:20.670
- No. thank you.
- What did you have in mind. your grace?

128
00:15:24.507 --> 00:15:27.844
I wish to propose a marriage
between your son. ser laenor...

129
00:15:28.803 --> 00:15:31.681
And my daughter and heir.
the Princess rhaenyra.

130
00:15:31.764 --> 00:15:35.226
It's long past time our houses
were united in blood.

131
00:15:35.309 --> 00:15:37.520
The last pillars of old valyria.

132
00:15:38.396 --> 00:15:41.983
You honor both me
and my house. your grace.

133
00:15:42.066 --> 00:15:45.236
There are certain details
I would wish clarified

134
00:15:45.319 --> 00:15:48.531
before the Princess rhaenys
and I could accept this most...

135
00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:50.867
Generous proposal.

136
00:15:52.535 --> 00:15:54.162
What details?

137
00:15:56.998 --> 00:16:00.585
We would like to know
how the succession will be handled.

138
00:16:03.880 --> 00:16:06.132
Rhaenyra is my heir.

139
00:16:06.215 --> 00:16:09.427
Upon my death. my throne and my titles
will pass to her.

140
00:16:09.510 --> 00:16:12.972
She and ser laenor's firstborn child.
regardless of gender.

141
00:16:13.055 --> 00:16:15.683
will inherit the iron throne from her.

142
00:16:17.602 --> 00:16:22.732
Can I presume that.
in keeping with westerosi tradition...

143
00:16:23.816 --> 00:16:26.444
Their children would take
their father's name?

144
00:16:27.904 --> 00:16:31.282
That they would be born velaryons?

145
00:16:31.365 --> 00:16:33.159
Surely. lord corlys.

146
00:16:33.242 --> 00:16:35.536
you are not proposing
the Targaryen dynasty

147
00:16:35.620 --> 00:16:38.331
end with my daughter
simply because she is a woman?

148
00:16:41.334 --> 00:16:43.961
I only seek clarity. your grace.

149
00:16:48.716 --> 00:16:50.301
Might I have a chair
brought in for you?

150
00:16:50.384 --> 00:16:51.385
I do not...

151
00:16:51.469 --> 00:16:53.429
No. I do not require a chair.

152
00:16:55.973 --> 00:17:00.102
Upon their birth.
ser laenor and rhaenyra's children

153
00:17:00.186 --> 00:17:02.647
shall take their
father's name. velaryon...

154
00:17:03.564 --> 00:17:06.609
In keeping with our traditions.

155
00:17:06.692 --> 00:17:08.194
However.

156
00:17:08.277 --> 00:17:12.073
at such time when their firstborn
ascends the iron throne.

157
00:17:12.156 --> 00:17:15.284
he or she will do so
bearing the name Targaryen.

158
00:17:16.911 --> 00:17:21.165
Dragons will rule the seven kingdoms
for the next hundred years.

159
00:17:21.249 --> 00:17:23.251
just as they did the last.

160
00:17:36.347 --> 00:17:38.349
This is an equitable compromise.

161
00:17:40.017 --> 00:17:41.227
Good.

162
00:17:42.103 --> 00:17:44.730
Now. if there's nothing further.

163
00:17:54.991 --> 00:17:59.328
In truth. if it had
to be someone. I'm glad it is you.

164
00:18:01.706 --> 00:18:04.333
I know this union is not
what you would choose.

165
00:18:05.585 --> 00:18:07.795
I hold nothing against you. cousin.

166
00:18:08.838 --> 00:18:10.256
No. I...

167
00:18:12.091 --> 00:18:13.301
Rather...

168
00:18:14.176 --> 00:18:16.804
Dare I say it is a matter of taste?

169
00:18:20.725 --> 00:18:23.728
I prefer roast duck to goose.

170
00:18:24.520 --> 00:18:26.147
I cannot say why.

171
00:18:29.692 --> 00:18:31.152
It's not for a lack of trying.

172
00:18:32.737 --> 00:18:34.947
There are those
who like goose very well.

173
00:18:36.699 --> 00:18:39.076
I find it a bit greasy for my taste.

174
00:18:43.414 --> 00:18:45.791
I know that whatever agreement
being struck up there

175
00:18:45.875 --> 00:18:47.835
will not change your appetites.

176
00:18:48.336 --> 00:18:50.338
nor will it change mine.

177
00:18:52.381 --> 00:18:53.424
And what do you propose?

178
00:18:59.805 --> 00:19:03.851
That we perform our duty to our fathers
and to the realm

179
00:19:03.934 --> 00:19:06.103
and when it's done...

180
00:19:06.187 --> 00:19:08.606
Each of us dines as we see fit.

181
00:19:19.241 --> 00:19:22.870
Viserys has taken
to bed while his ship is readied.

182
00:19:25.331 --> 00:19:26.666
Perhaps I...

183
00:19:27.625 --> 00:19:29.043
Overextended myself?

184
00:19:31.545 --> 00:19:32.963
Pushed him too close to the edge?

185
00:19:33.047 --> 00:19:35.841
My cousin chose to sail
into this tempest. husband.

186
00:19:37.718 --> 00:19:40.179
It was undignified of the king
to drag himself here

187
00:19:40.262 --> 00:19:42.598
and beg for laenor's hand.

188
00:19:43.015 --> 00:19:44.225
Where is laenor?

189
00:19:44.975 --> 00:19:47.436
He and rhaenyra
are walking the coast.

190
00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:48.521
Good.

191
00:19:49.313 --> 00:19:51.941
Do they seem... familiar?

192
00:19:52.733 --> 00:19:54.333
They grew up together.

193
00:19:55.152 --> 00:19:57.697
Familiarity is not at issue.

194
00:19:57.780 --> 00:20:00.825
I'm sure laenor
was already taken with her.

195
00:20:00.908 --> 00:20:02.827
She's grown quite comely
these last few years.

196
00:20:02.910 --> 00:20:04.704
You know his true nature.

197
00:20:06.122 --> 00:20:07.123
He's still young.

198
00:20:08.916 --> 00:20:10.084
He will outgrow it.

199
00:20:12.002 --> 00:20:14.547
There is no pleasure
in the world like...

200
00:20:16.674 --> 00:20:17.883
Bedding a woman.

201
00:20:17.967 --> 00:20:20.845
We are placing our son in danger.

202
00:20:21.762 --> 00:20:24.056
The lords of the realm
bent the knee to rhaenyra

203
00:20:24.140 --> 00:20:25.349
and swore obeisance to her.

204
00:20:25.433 --> 00:20:27.268
That was before there
was a true-born prince

205
00:20:27.351 --> 00:20:29.186
named aegon Targaryen.

206
00:20:29.270 --> 00:20:31.439
Rhaenyra's succession
will be challenged.

207
00:20:31.939 --> 00:20:35.776
Knives will come out for her.
her husband. and for their heirs.

208
00:20:35.860 --> 00:20:39.697
Our house controls the realm's Navy
and half its dragons.

209
00:20:39.780 --> 00:20:41.991
Anyone fool enough to challenge
rhaenyra's claim

210
00:20:42.074 --> 00:20:45.327
- will be crushed.
- To what end. corlys? Wealth? Power?

211
00:20:45.411 --> 00:20:47.037
- Pnde?
- Jusfice.

212
00:20:52.501 --> 00:20:54.044
By all rights.

213
00:20:54.128 --> 00:20:56.172
you should be
queen of the seven kingdoms.

214
00:20:58.257 --> 00:20:59.967
You were robbed
of the crown by...

215
00:21:00.050 --> 00:21:03.971
I never wore the crown
because the realm would not have it so.

216
00:21:04.054 --> 00:21:06.348
And I would remedy that

217
00:21:06.432 --> 00:21:10.019
small-minded error
by any means necessar...

218
00:21:10.102 --> 00:21:14.356
I myself have put the business
behind me. corlys.

219
00:21:22.406 --> 00:21:25.409
I've always feared the day
you'd have to marry a woman.

220
00:21:26.410 --> 00:21:27.620
And now it comes.

221
00:21:29.038 --> 00:21:30.831
Your betrothed gives you leave

222
00:21:30.915 --> 00:21:33.334
of her own free will
to continue partaking of.

223
00:21:34.084 --> 00:21:36.337
Was I the duck or the goose?

224
00:21:36.420 --> 00:21:38.839
I've come to meet my fate
and you make a jape of it?

225
00:21:40.508 --> 00:21:42.468
Look. rhaenyra will be
queen of the seven kingdoms

226
00:21:42.551 --> 00:21:44.762
and you will be her king consort.

227
00:21:45.763 --> 00:21:47.765
Think of the tournament.

228
00:21:47.848 --> 00:21:50.100
the feast. the battles at sea.

229
00:21:53.103 --> 00:21:54.939
Will you wear your crown today.
your grace?

230
00:21:57.483 --> 00:21:58.901
You're a fool.

231
00:22:06.242 --> 00:22:07.701
You will need a sworn protector.

232
00:22:08.494 --> 00:22:09.495
Hmm.

233
00:22:30.224 --> 00:22:32.852
This is better
than we could've hoped for.

234
00:22:38.107 --> 00:22:40.025
She has a paramour of her own.

235
00:22:42.862 --> 00:22:44.113
I wonder who it is.

236
00:23:07.636 --> 00:23:10.055
Did sleep flee you as well
this morning?

237
00:23:11.348 --> 00:23:13.225
I needed to see you. Princess.

238
00:23:14.226 --> 00:23:16.228
I confess
I had a similar desire.

239
00:23:21.525 --> 00:23:26.238
You have confided in me now and then
over the years of our acquaintance.

240
00:23:26.322 --> 00:23:32.912
I feel. forgive me.
that I know you... a bit.

241
00:23:35.331 --> 00:23:36.707
You know more than a bit.

242
00:23:40.294 --> 00:23:45.507
I've heard you say so many times
how you loathe the lot of your position.

243
00:23:46.133 --> 00:23:48.510
that you are to be married off
at your father's whim

244
00:23:48.594 --> 00:23:51.180
with no thought given to the yearning
of your own heart.

245
00:23:51.263 --> 00:23:53.891
and now the day comes.

246
00:23:55.559 --> 00:23:59.480
Ser laenor is a good and decent man.
but you did not choose him.

247
00:24:00.481 --> 00:24:03.901
- He was chosen for you.
- That's true.

248
00:24:07.279 --> 00:24:09.281
If there were another path...

249
00:24:10.366 --> 00:24:12.368
One that led to freedom...

250
00:24:13.035 --> 00:24:14.286
Would you tread it?

251
00:24:16.038 --> 00:24:18.582
Rhaenyra. before I came here.

252
00:24:18.666 --> 00:24:20.876
I was a knight in the stormlands.

253
00:24:21.627 --> 00:24:23.837
I have deep knowledge
of the port at sunspear

254
00:24:23.921 --> 00:24:26.048
where I've seen the ships
of essos setting sail

255
00:24:26.131 --> 00:24:28.509
with their hulls full
of oranges and cinnamon

256
00:24:28.592 --> 00:24:30.803
and I've always wished
to see where they went.

257
00:24:32.721 --> 00:24:34.348
Are you asking for leave?

258
00:24:35.724 --> 00:24:38.268
I'm asking you to come with me...

259
00:24:39.812 --> 00:24:41.814
Away from all of this.

260
00:24:42.523 --> 00:24:45.484
From the burdens and indignities
of your inheritance.

261
00:24:45.567 --> 00:24:48.988
Let us leave it all behind
and see the world together...

262
00:24:50.781 --> 00:24:52.282
Where we'll be nameless.

263
00:24:52.366 --> 00:24:53.993
and free...

264
00:24:54.910 --> 00:24:57.413
Free to go where we like.
to love as we like.

265
00:24:59.123 --> 00:25:00.541
In essos...

266
00:25:03.335 --> 00:25:04.962
You could marry me.

267
00:25:08.841 --> 00:25:10.592
A marriage for love.

268
00:25:10.676 --> 00:25:12.428
not for the crown.

269
00:25:37.411 --> 00:25:40.330
I am the crown. ser criston.

270
00:25:42.791 --> 00:25:43.917
Or I will be.

271
00:25:45.878 --> 00:25:48.464
I may chafe at my duties.

272
00:25:48.547 --> 00:25:51.717
but do you think I would choose infamy

273
00:25:51.800 --> 00:25:55.471
in exchange for a bushel of oranges
or a ship to asshai?

274
00:25:58.891 --> 00:26:00.267
It is my duty

275
00:26:00.350 --> 00:26:03.437
to marry a nobleman from a great house

276
00:26:03.520 --> 00:26:06.065
and ser laenor will make a fine husband.

277
00:26:10.527 --> 00:26:12.446
But my. um...

278
00:26:13.447 --> 00:26:15.074
My marriage...

279
00:26:16.408 --> 00:26:18.577
Does not have to be the end.

280
00:26:21.455 --> 00:26:26.418
Ser criston. laenor and I have
an understanding.

281
00:26:28.170 --> 00:26:32.091
I've granted him leave
to pursue his own interests...

282
00:26:33.133 --> 00:26:35.094
And in turn. he's granted me the same.

283
00:26:42.351 --> 00:26:44.186
So you want me to be your whore?

284
00:26:46.146 --> 00:26:49.608
I want us
to continue as we began.

285
00:26:49.691 --> 00:26:53.195
with you as my sworn protector.
my white knight.

286
00:26:53.278 --> 00:26:55.197
I took an oath.

287
00:26:56.949 --> 00:27:00.327
As a knight of your kingsguard.

288
00:27:00.410 --> 00:27:02.371
An oath of chastity. I've broken it.

289
00:27:02.454 --> 00:27:04.957
- I won't tell anyone...
- I've soiled my white cloak.

290
00:27:05.040 --> 00:27:07.292
And it's the only thing
I have to my fucking name!

291
00:27:10.546 --> 00:27:13.966
I thought if we were married.
I might be able to restore it.

292
00:27:20.889 --> 00:27:22.933
The iron throne looms larger than me.

293
00:27:23.016 --> 00:27:26.603
larger than anyone in my family.

294
00:27:26.687 --> 00:27:30.315
Aegon the conqueror
united the seven kingdoms

295
00:27:30.399 --> 00:27:32.401
and put them on a path...

296
00:27:33.110 --> 00:27:34.486
Ser criston.

297
00:28:20.365 --> 00:28:21.365
[Fihuds]

298
00:28:22.409 --> 00:28:23.887
- Fetch the maester!
- Get back.

299
00:28:23.911 --> 00:28:25.662
Get mellos! Get back!

300
00:28:25.746 --> 00:28:27.372
Prepare the crucible.

301
00:28:28.540 --> 00:28:30.375
We'll need leeches.

302
00:28:34.254 --> 00:28:35.672
Ser criston...

303
00:28:37.090 --> 00:28:38.508
You've been summoned.

304
00:28:39.885 --> 00:28:42.095
I left the princessjust minutes ago.

305
00:28:43.013 --> 00:28:44.598
Not the Princess. ser.

306
00:28:45.265 --> 00:28:46.350
The queen.

307
00:29:01.281 --> 00:29:02.908
Ser criston. your grace.

308
00:29:07.204 --> 00:29:08.830
That will be all.

309
00:29:22.219 --> 00:29:25.722
I fear I must question you
on a delicate matter. ser criston.

310
00:29:28.767 --> 00:29:30.978
I am your servant as always. my queen.

311
00:29:32.521 --> 00:29:34.731
It concerns our dear Princess rhaenyra.

312
00:29:36.066 --> 00:29:37.276
Please.

313
00:30:03.385 --> 00:30:06.638
You are her sworn protector
and rightly loyal to her.

314
00:30:07.764 --> 00:30:09.308
I am.

315
00:30:13.145 --> 00:30:15.147
The night of daemon's return...

316
00:30:17.899 --> 00:30:19.526
There's been a rumor...

317
00:30:20.444 --> 00:30:25.073
Or rather. my father received
an accounting of...

318
00:30:26.658 --> 00:30:29.244
A lapse of morals

319
00:30:29.328 --> 00:30:33.332
that may have occurred between...

320
00:30:36.418 --> 00:30:39.588
It is. of course. unthinkable for me
to question the virtue of the Princess.

321
00:30:39.671 --> 00:30:41.631
whom I hold in highest regard.

322
00:30:41.715 --> 00:30:46.011
but. I did. however. wonder if...

323
00:30:53.352 --> 00:30:56.563
I'm not unaware
that in flush of youth...

324
00:30:57.564 --> 00:30:59.191
There may be errors made...

325
00:31:00.484 --> 00:31:03.153
Breaches in resolve.

326
00:31:03.236 --> 00:31:06.239
- Breaches. or rather lapses...
- It happened. your grace.

327
00:31:11.912 --> 00:31:13.914
The sin you allude to.

328
00:31:16.917 --> 00:31:18.251
I have committed it.

329
00:31:22.089 --> 00:31:25.092
At her instigation.
it is true. but that should...

330
00:31:26.259 --> 00:31:27.886
It is no excuse.

331
00:31:30.764 --> 00:31:32.432
My oath has been broken.

332
00:31:33.433 --> 00:31:35.060
I have dishonored myself.

333
00:31:36.728 --> 00:31:38.730
I deserve no consideration.

334
00:31:42.901 --> 00:31:44.111
But if...

335
00:31:45.237 --> 00:31:49.741
As a clement queen.
you are inclined to pity...

336
00:31:51.118 --> 00:31:52.744
I would ask only this...

337
00:31:55.247 --> 00:31:57.833
That rather than gelding me

338
00:31:57.916 --> 00:32:00.085
and having me tortured

339
00:32:00.877 --> 00:32:03.880
you would sentence me
mercifully to death.

340
00:32:19.563 --> 00:32:21.523
Thank you for your honesty. ser criston.

341
00:32:32.033 --> 00:32:33.160
You may go.

342
00:33:04.316 --> 00:33:07.944
Rest now. your grace.
I will bring the leeches.

343
00:33:08.028 --> 00:33:10.655
Uh. if I may. grand maester.

344
00:33:10.739 --> 00:33:14.284
I took the Liberty
of preparing a fresh set

345
00:33:14.367 --> 00:33:18.455
of herbal poultices
that might be more effective.

346
00:33:18.538 --> 00:33:21.041
That will not be necessary.
onivyle.

347
00:33:21.124 --> 00:33:24.544
The leechings have always brought
his grace relief.

348
00:33:43.772 --> 00:33:44.856
To help him sleep.

349
00:33:56.284 --> 00:33:57.494
Where's the queen?

350
00:34:00.247 --> 00:34:03.333
I was given to understand that she
is othennise occupied. your grace.

351
00:34:23.770 --> 00:34:25.939
Will I be remembered
as a good king. lyonel?

352
00:34:27.983 --> 00:34:29.192
Your grace?

353
00:34:30.277 --> 00:34:33.822
What will they say of me
when the histories are written?

354
00:34:34.739 --> 00:34:37.325
I have neither fought nor conquered.

355
00:34:37.409 --> 00:34:39.703
nor suffered any great defeat.

356
00:34:41.705 --> 00:34:44.332
Some might call that good fortune.

357
00:34:46.835 --> 00:34:49.796
It hardly makes a good song. does it?

358
00:34:49.879 --> 00:34:52.716
To be sung at feasts
in a hundred years...

359
00:34:52.799 --> 00:34:54.426
Five hundred.

360
00:34:57.762 --> 00:35:00.640
You have carried
king jaehaerys's legacy.

361
00:35:01.641 --> 00:35:04.060
And kept the realm strong.

362
00:35:04.477 --> 00:35:06.163
Is it not better
to live in peace

363
00:35:06.187 --> 00:35:09.190
than to have songs
sung after you are dead?

364
00:35:10.025 --> 00:35:11.026
Perhaps.

365
00:35:13.278 --> 00:35:16.281
But there is a part of me
wishes I'd been tested.

366
00:35:17.741 --> 00:35:20.368
I often think that in the crucible.

367
00:35:20.452 --> 00:35:23.079
I may have been forged a different man.

368
00:35:25.081 --> 00:35:29.502
Many that are tested.
only wish to have been spared it.

369
00:35:31.796 --> 00:35:34.591
Another lord might assure me
that I would rise like

370
00:35:34.674 --> 00:35:36.551
aegon the conqueror given the chance.

371
00:35:36.635 --> 00:35:38.675
- Your grace. that is...
- You're right.

372
00:35:38.928 --> 00:35:41.931
You're right as always.

373
00:35:44.643 --> 00:35:47.270
It is perhaps best not to know.

374
00:36:34.984 --> 00:36:36.986
It is with great pleasure

375
00:36:37.070 --> 00:36:40.365
that his grace. king viserys.
announces the start

376
00:36:40.448 --> 00:36:43.076
of the royal wedding celebrations.

377
00:36:44.994 --> 00:36:49.290
House Lannister with their lord.
Jason Lannister.

378
00:36:49.374 --> 00:36:53.461
Lord Paramount of the west.
and master of casterly rock.

379
00:36:54.671 --> 00:36:58.299
House hightower
with their lord. hobert hightower.

380
00:36:58.383 --> 00:37:01.553
Beacon of the south.
defender of the citadel.

381
00:37:01.636 --> 00:37:02.762
the voice of oldtown...

382
00:37:15.775 --> 00:37:17.569
Congratulations. your grace.

383
00:37:17.652 --> 00:37:19.696
You have made a fine match
for the Princess.

384
00:37:19.779 --> 00:37:21.656
Thank you. lord Jason.

385
00:37:21.740 --> 00:37:23.825
I could think of no better man
than ser laenor.

386
00:37:25.243 --> 00:37:27.912
Well. if this is only the welcome feast.

387
00:37:27.996 --> 00:37:31.499
I admit. I cannot imagine what you might
have planned for the wedding.

388
00:37:31.583 --> 00:37:34.002
My daughter is the future queen.

389
00:37:35.128 --> 00:37:37.922
I wanted this to be
a wedding for the histories.

390
00:37:39.466 --> 00:37:40.842
Where is the queen?

391
00:37:40.925 --> 00:37:43.136
I had hoped to pay my respects.

392
00:37:44.679 --> 00:37:48.850
I understand the queen is still
readying herself for the celebrations.

393
00:37:48.933 --> 00:37:51.144
This is why men wage war

394
00:37:51.936 --> 00:37:54.439
because women would never
be ready for the battle in time.

395
00:37:59.611 --> 00:38:02.238
Your presence is always
such a pleasure. lord Jason.

396
00:38:02.322 --> 00:38:05.158
Princess. your grace.

397
00:38:15.335 --> 00:38:19.672
Your grace. Princess rhaenyra.
congratulations are in order.

398
00:38:20.423 --> 00:38:23.218
We are very honored
to have you as a guest. ser gerold.

399
00:38:23.301 --> 00:38:25.261
I must say. I was most distressed

400
00:38:25.345 --> 00:38:28.348
to hear of the lady rhea's
tragic passing.

401
00:38:29.140 --> 00:38:30.767
I'm very sorry for your loss.

402
00:38:30.850 --> 00:38:33.186
Lady rhea
was a unique character.

403
00:38:33.812 --> 00:38:36.898
Her kind is not soon to be seen again.

404
00:38:36.981 --> 00:38:40.401
If there is anything the crown might do
to aid house Royce...

405
00:38:48.409 --> 00:38:51.371
Lord corlys of house velaryon.

406
00:38:51.454 --> 00:38:54.082
Lord of the tides. master of driftmark.

407
00:38:54.165 --> 00:38:57.961
And his lady wife.
Princess rhaenys Targaryen.

408
00:38:58.044 --> 00:39:01.506
And their son and heir.
ser laenor velaryon.

409
00:39:01.589 --> 00:39:04.217
the future king consort.

410
00:39:45.508 --> 00:39:47.802
- My betrothed.
- My betrothed.

411
00:41:11.552 --> 00:41:15.556
Be welcome.
as we join together in celebration.

412
00:41:16.933 --> 00:41:18.518
Tonight is only its beginning.

413
00:41:19.394 --> 00:41:21.980
We honor the crown's oldest

414
00:41:22.063 --> 00:41:25.191
and fiercest ally. house velaryon.

415
00:41:27.735 --> 00:41:32.407
Reaching back to the days of old valyria
and the age of dragons.

416
00:41:34.575 --> 00:41:37.578
With house Targaryen and...

417
00:42:16.409 --> 00:42:18.077
The king will not be happy.

418
00:42:18.161 --> 00:42:20.329
Right in the midst of his speech.

419
00:42:31.549 --> 00:42:33.926
The beacon on the hightower.

420
00:42:34.010 --> 00:42:37.847
do you know what color it glows
when oldtown calls its banners to war?

421
00:42:38.806 --> 00:42:40.016
Green.

422
00:42:51.819 --> 00:42:53.279
Congratulations. stepdaughter.

423
00:42:54.614 --> 00:42:56.032
What a blessing this is for you.

424
00:43:08.503 --> 00:43:09.837
Please be seated.

425
00:43:19.347 --> 00:43:20.431
Where was I?

426
00:43:20.515 --> 00:43:22.433
The joining of the two houses.
your grace.

427
00:43:22.517 --> 00:43:23.976
Yeah.

428
00:43:25.394 --> 00:43:26.813
Yes.

429
00:43:32.276 --> 00:43:37.865
With house Targaryen
and house velaryon united.

430
00:43:37.949 --> 00:43:41.994
I hope to herald in
a second age of dragons

431
00:43:42.078 --> 00:43:43.496
in Westeros.

432
00:43:54.132 --> 00:43:57.135
And after
tonight's small affair...

433
00:43:59.679 --> 00:44:03.057
Seven days
of tournament and feasting.

434
00:44:06.269 --> 00:44:07.895
At the end of it all...

435
00:44:09.063 --> 00:44:12.483
At the end of it all. a royal wedding...

436
00:44:13.526 --> 00:44:14.902
Between my daughter.

437
00:44:15.862 --> 00:44:17.071
my heir...

438
00:44:17.822 --> 00:44:19.031
Your future queen...

439
00:44:20.324 --> 00:44:24.162
And ser laenor velaryon.
the heir to driftmark.

440
00:45:16.923 --> 00:45:18.523
I was never much of a dancer.

441
00:45:18.591 --> 00:45:19.943
It's not much different to combat.

442
00:45:19.967 --> 00:45:22.303
Hmm.
I shall hope for a different outcome.

443
00:46:36.294 --> 00:46:39.672
- Your grace.
- We thank you for coming. uncle.

444
00:46:39.755 --> 00:46:42.383
I worried that given leave of your
father's shadow.

445
00:46:42.466 --> 00:46:44.677
you might wither
in king's landing's sun.

446
00:46:45.803 --> 00:46:47.805
But you stood tall.

447
00:46:49.015 --> 00:46:50.975
Know that oldtown stands with you.

448
00:47:18.127 --> 00:47:22.173
In the vale.
men are made to answer for their crimes.

449
00:47:24.633 --> 00:47:26.802
Even targaryens.

450
00:47:26.886 --> 00:47:27.970
Who are you?

451
00:47:28.054 --> 00:47:31.057
Ser gerold Royce of runestone.

452
00:47:32.808 --> 00:47:34.185
And?

453
00:47:42.902 --> 00:47:46.489
I am cousin to your late lady wife.

454
00:47:46.572 --> 00:47:49.700
Ah. yes. Terrible thing.

455
00:47:49.784 --> 00:47:53.079
I'm positively bereft.
Such a tragic accident.

456
00:47:53.162 --> 00:47:56.123
You know better than anyone.
it was no accident.

457
00:47:56.207 --> 00:47:58.167
Are you confessing some guilt.
ser gerold?

458
00:47:58.250 --> 00:48:01.045
I am making an accusation.

459
00:48:03.756 --> 00:48:07.176
In king's landing. men are made
to answer for their slanders.

460
00:48:07.259 --> 00:48:09.053
Even old bronze cunts like you.

461
00:48:11.639 --> 00:48:13.039
The truth is. I'm glad you've come.

462
00:48:13.099 --> 00:48:15.351
I wish to speak to you
about my inheritance.

463
00:48:16.519 --> 00:48:19.480
- What inheritance?
- Lady rhea and I had no heirs.

464
00:48:19.563 --> 00:48:22.775
As her husband. whatever she was due
now passes to me.

465
00:48:24.443 --> 00:48:28.906
She stood to inherit all of runestone.
Did she not?

466
00:48:32.410 --> 00:48:34.578
After my niece's wedding.
I plan to fly to the eyrie

467
00:48:34.662 --> 00:48:36.205
and petition lady jeyne myself.

468
00:48:36.288 --> 00:48:38.290
Perhaps I'll see you there. ser gerold.

469
00:49:52.281 --> 00:49:55.284
Has anybody ever told you
you're nearly as pretty as your brother?

470
00:49:55.367 --> 00:49:58.162
You flatter me. my prince.

471
00:49:58.245 --> 00:49:59.914
I was sorry to hear
about your lady wife.

472
00:49:59.997 --> 00:50:01.665
Don't be. I wasn't.

473
00:50:01.749 --> 00:50:03.501
My lady was never very kind to me.

474
00:50:03.584 --> 00:50:05.127
I know who it is.

475
00:50:06.253 --> 00:50:08.214
The handsome paramour.

476
00:50:08.297 --> 00:50:09.298
Who?

477
00:50:10.216 --> 00:50:11.842
Ser criston Cole.

478
00:50:12.593 --> 00:50:15.804
- Her sworn protector?
- Look at him.

479
00:50:15.888 --> 00:50:17.640
The man is fully cunt-struck.

480
00:50:18.766 --> 00:50:22.770
A Targaryen prince.
a dashing knight. and a dragonrider.

481
00:50:22.853 --> 00:50:24.605
You appear to be every
young maiden's dream.

482
00:50:24.688 --> 00:50:26.607
That's only because
you don't know me yet.

483
00:50:26.690 --> 00:50:29.068
I believe ser criston has bloodied
that white cloak of his

484
00:50:29.151 --> 00:50:31.487
- with your bride's maidenhead.
- Keep your voice down.

485
00:50:31.570 --> 00:50:33.781
Perhaps that is something
we might remedy. my prince.

486
00:50:33.864 --> 00:50:34.865
Perhaps it is.

487
00:50:36.367 --> 00:50:38.994
This is a good thing.
She knows your secret.

488
00:50:40.204 --> 00:50:41.455
and now you know hers.

489
00:50:47.795 --> 00:50:48.879
Hey!

490
00:50:55.427 --> 00:50:56.554
Hey!

491
00:51:12.111 --> 00:51:14.113
They make a handsome match. don't they?

492
00:51:14.989 --> 00:51:16.282
What?

493
00:51:17.116 --> 00:51:19.118
The Princess and ser laenor.

494
00:51:22.496 --> 00:51:23.581
Hey!

495
00:51:28.711 --> 00:51:30.129
Ser Joffrey lonmouth.

496
00:51:31.130 --> 00:51:32.881
or the knight of kisses. they call me.

497
00:51:32.965 --> 00:51:35.593
though I don't know why.

498
00:51:36.302 --> 00:51:38.029
I'm on watch.
What's your business?

499
00:51:38.053 --> 00:51:40.764
You don't know me. ser criston.

500
00:51:40.848 --> 00:51:43.434
But we are both deeply
invested in this union.

501
00:51:43.517 --> 00:51:44.685
Hey!

502
00:51:46.395 --> 00:51:49.565
If you have something to say.
ser Joffrey. speak it.

503
00:51:49.648 --> 00:51:51.650
Ser laenor is quite dear to me.

504
00:51:52.818 --> 00:51:55.988
As I know the Princess is to you.

505
00:51:57.990 --> 00:52:00.451
We should swear
to each other to guard them.

506
00:52:00.534 --> 00:52:04.121
and their secrets.
because if those are kept safe...

507
00:52:06.749 --> 00:52:07.791
Then so are we all.

508
00:52:29.271 --> 00:52:30.272
Hey!

509
00:52:52.252 --> 00:52:54.838
- May I. ser hannin?
- Of course. my prince.

510
00:53:04.056 --> 00:53:05.057
Hey!

511
00:53:59.528 --> 00:54:00.654
Hey!

512
00:54:13.751 --> 00:54:15.335
What in the seven hells is going on?

513
00:54:17.004 --> 00:54:18.422
Laenoh

514
